rt a business. Example: cooking, making batik, reflexology, hairdressing or herbal medicine.</li>\r\n	<li>Create economically independent villages with one basic form of business. Example: An economically independent village with herbal medicine as its main business.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'What We Do', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '417-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-24 10:31:09', '2014-06-24 03:31:09', '', 417, 'http://perbanas.org/en/417-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
