(1437, 1, '2014-12-04 11:43:28', '2014-12-04 04:43:28', '<h2 style="margin-top: 0;">PERBANAS COUNCIL ( DIVISION )</h2>\r\n\r\n<div id="secretary-general" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>1. Secretary General</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Support the Work Programs of all Divisions.</li>\r\n	<li>Organize regular Board Meetings and Plenary Meetings.</li>\r\n	<li>Activate KMPP.</li>\r\n	<li>Strengthen the Secretariat.</li>\r\n	<li>Drafting of the Secretariat Work Manual.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="treasurer" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>2. Treasurer</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Consolidation of regional financial statements.</li>\r\n	<li>Make changes to the ‘chart of account’.</li>\r\n	<li>Evaluate YPP accounts.</li>\r\n	<li>Send audit reports to members.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="organization-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>3. Organization Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Discourse to unify all regional banking activities into one organization which is Perbanas.</li>\r\n	<li>Regional Perbanas offices should be led by representatives of large banks / state-owned enterprises or CEOs of banks with head offices in regions.</li>\r\n	<li>“Synchronization of the Strategies and Activities of Central and Regional Perbanas (mandate of congress)” is perceived as ‘mirroring’ of Central Perbanas and is the key to the success of other programs.</li>\r\n	<li>Establishment of CEO Forum tailored to each group of banks.</li>\r\n	<li>Increase coordination between Banking organizations and Professions, involving IBI, Himbara, Asbanda, Asbisindo, and ASPI.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordination with Perbarindo can be done once a year to optimize linkage program.</li>\r\n	<li>Synchronization of events held in each banking association so as not to coincide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="rnd-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>4. Research &amp; Development Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Routine FGD (<em>hot issue</em>) once a month\r\na. Hearing with the House of Representatives\r\nb. FGD with Associations\r\nc. FGD on the Fee of Indonesian Financial Services Authority with Nonbank Institutions.\r\nd. FGD on Bank Conglomeration\r\ne. FGD on Banking Laws\r\nf. FGD on Outsourcing</li>\r\n	<li>Daily info (regulations / <em>hot issue</em>)</li>\r\n	<li>Assessment on Banking Efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>Financial Inclusion</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of the banking industry in facing MEA</li>\r\n	<li>Socialization of policies</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="academic-and-human-resource-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>5. Academic &amp; Human Resource Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Optimize the ‘link and match’ process with Perbanas Institute and STIE Perbanas Surabaya.</li>\r\n	<li>Actively provide input and propositions on National Health Insurance and provisions on outsourcing.</li>\r\n	<li>Availability of reliable human resource and technology system (in relation to the availability of human resources in the field of IT).</li>\r\n	<li>Support and actively participate in the banking and financial industry, specifically in addressing the ASEAN open market era in 2015 as well as encourage regulators in relation to the recruitment process of human resources in the banking and financial industry with a standardization and profession qualification which have been complied by Perbanas, IBI, and LSPP especially for foreign human resources in the upcoming open market era.</li>\r\n	<li>Involve and get involved in activities which are done in coordination with the regional Perbanas.</li>\r\n	<li>Strengthen the position of Perbanas as a working partner to regulators, specifically in drafting regulations related to human resources in the banking and financial industry, so as to present a good bargaining position for the association and the banking industry in general.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="foreign-affairs-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>6. Foreign Affairs Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Establishment of “ASEAN One Integration” Committee</li>\r\n	<li>Gathering of information from various sources (Mr. Raden Pardede, Secretary General of ASEAN and BI) prior to the drafting of ‘Position Paper’ / ‘Working Paper’ which will be addressed at the ASEAN Banking Association annual event in Myanmar on 14-15 November 2013, Research and Development Division is hoped to assist in providing material related to the ASEAN Economic Community.</li>\r\n	<li>Based on the information gathered, a framework will be formulated which will be used as a reference for the drafting of ‘Position Paper’ / ‘Working Paper’ by Perbanas internal parties or to be handed over to another party (outsourcing). Several parties considered able to assist in the drafting of ‘Position Paper’ / ‘Working Paper’ is MM-UI, Mckinsey &amp; Company (Indonesia), Boston Consultant Group or other consultants.</li>\r\n	<li>Gathering of information from Perbanas members who have access to their holding banks in ASEAN countries, on regulations or initiatives which have or are being applied by banks in each ASEAN country, in preparation to face the ASEAN Economic Community 2020.</li>\r\n	<li>The Foreign Affairs Division will invite as many Perbanas members as possible to participate in the ABA Annual Meeting in Myanmar on 14-15 November 2013. Aside from participating in the Annual Meeting, participants will be able to explore the chances of building a business network in Myanmar.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="law-and-regulation-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>7. Law &amp; Regulations Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiative:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Increase legal protection for the banking industry by establishing Perbanas Legal Working Commission and synergize with BI initiatives.</li>\r\n	<li>Legal advocacy for members.</li>\r\n	<li>Expert witness if needed.</li>\r\n	<li>Provide database related to antifraud matters.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="governance-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>8. Governance Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Socialization on GCG in cooperation with KNKG or BI (3 x a year).</li>\r\n	<li>Socialization on ASEAN Score Card in cooperation with a third party (1 x a year).</li>\r\n	<li>Determine a standard GCG format specifically for Medium-Small Banks.</li>\r\n	<li>Finalization of GCG Guidelines in the Banking Sector.</li>\r\n	<li>Bank Indonesia version of GCG Score procedure.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="tech-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>9. Technology Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Formulate a database for the Indonesian banking industry.</li>\r\n	<li>Architecture of Financial Services Transaction System and National Payment System.</li>\r\n	<li>Availability of reliable human resources and technology system.</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation on the establishment of consumer information bureau / Credit Information Management Institution (LPIP).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="pr-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>10. Public Relations Division</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Maintain the image and existence of Perbanas as an organization and become a reliable partner to stakeholders.</li>\r\n	<li>Provide reliable banking information to all stakeholders.</li>\r\n	<li>Effective and informative media communication programs through Perbanas spokes-person, provide key messages, cooperate with the media, website, and other social information tools.</li>\r\n	<li>A sustainable banking education program through cooperation with BI and the Indonesian Financial Services Authority.</li>\r\n	<li>Banking CSR programs with a focus on education and community empowerment.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="sharia-banking-compartment" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>11. Sharia Banking Compartment</h3>\r\nKey Initiatives:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Product Manager Forum.</li>\r\n	<li>Syariah Goes to Campus.</li>\r\n	<li>Syariah Award.</li>\r\n	<li>Syariah Banking IB Net.</li>\r\n	<li>Syariah Banker Certification.</li>\r\n	<li>IBEX Participation.</li>\r\n	<li>Legal Studies on Syariah Banking.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;', 'How We Work', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '419-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-04 11:43:28', '2014-12-04 04:43:28', '', 419, 'http://perbanas.org/id/419-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1438, 1, '2014-12-04 11:49:27', '2014-12-04 04:49:27', '<h2 style="margin-top: 0;">PENGURUS PERBANAS ( BIDANG )</h2>\r\n\r\n<div id="secretary-general" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>1.    Sekretaris Jenderal</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Support program kerja bidang.</li>\r\n	<li>Penyelenggaraan rapat rutin pengurus dan rapat pleno.</li>\r\n	<li>Mengaktifkan KMPP.</li>\r\n	<li>Penguatan sekretariat.</li>\r\n	<li>Penyusunan manual kerja sekretariat.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="treasurer" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>2.    Bendahara</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Konsolidasi laporan keuangan daerah.</li>\r\n	<li>Melakukan perubahan<em> chart of account</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Evaluasi rekening-rekening YPP.</li>\r\n	<li>Laporan audit agar dikirimkan ke anggota.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="organization-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>3.    Bidang Organisasi</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Wacana untuk menyatukan seluruh kegiatan perbankan daerah dalam satu wadah saja yaitu Perbanas.</li>\r\n	<li>Perbanas Daerah sebaiknya dipimpin oleh perwakilan Bank-Bank Besar/BUMN atau CEO bank yang berkantor pusat di daerah.</li>\r\n	<li>“Sinkronisasi Strategi dan Kegiatan Pusat dan Perbanas Daerah (Amanat Kongres)” merupakan <em>mirroring</em> dari Perbanas Pusat dan merupakan kunci utama keberhasilan program-program lainnya.</li>\r\n	<li>Pembentukan CEO Forum disesuaikan dengan kelompok-kelompok banknya.</li>\r\n	<li>Meningkatkan koordinasi antar organisasi Perbankan dan Profesi dengan melibatkan IBI, Himbara, Asbanda, Asbisindo, dan ASPI.</li>\r\n	<li>Kegiatan Probank yang dirancang disederhanakan saja acaranya.</li>\r\n	<li>Koordinasi dengan Perbarindo bisa setiap tahun sekali dilakukan untuk mengoptimalkan <em>linkage program</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Sinkronisasi waktu acara-acara di masing-masing asosiasi bank-bank agar tidak tumpang-tindih.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="rnd-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>4.    Bidang Pengkajian dan Pengembangan</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>FGD rutin (hot issue) setiap bulan sekali\r\na. RDP dengan DPR\r\nb. FGD dengan Asosiasi\r\nc. FGD Fee OJK dengan Lembaga Nonbank\r\nd. FGD Konglomerasi Bank\r\ne. FGD RUU Perbankan\r\nf. FGD Alih Daya</li>\r\n	<li>Info harian (peraturan / hot issue)</li>\r\n	<li>Kajian Efisiensi Perbankan</li>\r\n	<li>Financial Inclusion</li>\r\n	<li>Kesiapan Perbankan menghadapi MEA</li>\r\n	<li>Sosialisasi Kebijakan</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div id="academic-and-human-resource-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>4.    Bidang Pendidikan dan Pengembangan SDM</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Meningkatkan proses <em>link and match</em> dengan Perbanas Institute dan STIE Perbanas Surabaya.</li>\r\n	<li>Aktif memberikan masukan dan usulan mengenai Jamkesmas dan ketentuan <em>outsourcing</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketersediaan SDM dan Sistem Teknologi yang handal (terkait dengan ketersediaan tenaga SDM di bidang IT).</li>\r\n	<li>Mendorong dan berperan aktif dalam industry perbankan dan keuangan, khususnya menyikapi era pasar terbuka ASEAN tahun 2015 serta turut serta mendorong regulator terkait proses rekurtmen tenaga SDM bidang perbankan dan keuangan dengan suatu standarisasi dan kualifikasi profesi perbankan yang telah disusun oleh Perbanas, IBI, dan LSPP khususnya bagi tenaga kerja asing dalam era pasar terbuka mendatang.</li>\r\n	<li>Melibatkan dan terlibat dalam kegiatan-kegiatan yang dilakukan bersama dengan Perbanas Daerah.</li>\r\n	<li>Memperkuat posisi Perbanas sebagai mitra kerja regulator, khususnya terkait dengan penentuan suatu kebijakan terkait SDM di industry perbankan dan keuangan sehingga dapat memberi posisi tawar yang cukup baik bagi asosiasi dan perbankan pada umumnya.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="foreign-affairs-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>5.    Bidang Luar Negeri</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Pembentukan Komite “ASEAN One Integration”</li>\r\n	<li>Pengumpulan informasi dari beberapa sumber (Bpk. Raden Pardede, Sekjen ASEAN dan BI) sebelum melangkah untuk pembuatan <em>“Position Paper” / “Working Paper”</em> yang akan dipaparkan dalam acara tahunan ASEAN Banking Association di Myanmar tanggal 14-15 November 2013, Bidang Pengkajian dan Pengembangan diharapkan dapat membantu memberikan bahan-bahan yang terkait dengan Masyarakat Ekonomi ASEAN.</li>\r\n	<li>Atas dasar informasi-informasi yang terkumpul akan dibuat kerangka kerja yang akan dipergunakan sebagai acuan pembuatan <em>Position Paper/Working Paper</em> oleh internal Perbanas atau diserahkan kepada pihak lain (<em>outsource</em>). Beberapa pihak yang dipertimbangkan dapat membantu pembuatan <em>Position Paper/Working Paper</em> adalah MM-UI, Mckinsey &amp; Company (Indonesia), Boston Consultant Group atau konsultan lain.</li>\r\n	<li>Perlu dicari dari sumber anggota Perbanas yang memiliki akses ke bank-bank induknya di negara-negara ASEAN mengenai peraturan-peraturan atau inisiatip-inisiatip yang sudah / sedang dilakukan oleh bank-bank di masing-masing negara ASEAN tersebut dalam upaya mereka menghadapi ASEAN Economic Community 2020.</li>\r\n	<li>Bidang Luar Negeri akan mengundang sebanyak mungkin peserta dari anggota Perbanas untuk hadir dalam acara ABA Annual Meeting di Myanmar 14-15 November 2013. Selain menghadiri acara Annual Meeting para peserta dapat melakukan eksplorasi kemungkinan membangun jaringan bisnis di Myanmar.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="law-and-regulation-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>6.    Bidang Hukum</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Meningkatkan perlindungan hukum bagi industry perbankan dengan membentuk Komisi Kerja Legal Perbanas dan bersinergi dengan inisiatif BI.</li>\r\n	<li>Advokasi permasalahan hukum yang dihadapi oleh anggota.</li>\r\n	<li>Saksi ahli apabila diperlukan.</li>\r\n	<li>Menyediakan <em>database</em> yang terkait dengan <em>antifraud</em>.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="governance-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>7.    Bidang Governance</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Sosialisasi tentang GCG bekerja sama dengan KNKG atau BI (3 x setahun).</li>\r\n	<li>Sosialisasi <em>ASEAN Score Card</em> bekerja sama dengan pihak ke-3 (1 x setahun).</li>\r\n	<li>Membuat standar format GCG khusus untuk Bank Menengah-Kecil.</li>\r\n	<li>Finalisasi Pedoman GCG Sektor Perbankan.</li>\r\n	<li>Tata cara penilaian GCG <em>Score</em> versi Bank Indonesia.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="tech-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>8.   Bidang Teknologi</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Membentuk Database Perbankan Indonesia.</li>\r\n	<li>Arsitektur Sistem Transaksi Jasa Keuangan &amp; Sistem Pembayaran Nasional.</li>\r\n	<li>Ketersediaan SDM &amp; Sistem Teknologi yang handal.</li>\r\n	<li>Persiapan pembentukan biro informasi konsumen / Lembaga Pengelola Informasi Perkreditan (LPIP).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="pr-division" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>9.   Bidang Hubungan Masyarakat</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Menjaga citra dan eksistensi Perbanas sebagai organisasi serta menjadi mitra yang terpercaya bagi <em>stakeholders</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Menyampaikan informasi perbankan kepada seluruh <em>stakeholders</em> secara berimbang dan terpercaya.</li>\r\n	<li>Program media komunikasi yang efektif dan informatif melalui spokepersons Perbanas, menyediakan <em>key messages</em>, kerja sama dengan media, website, dan sarana sosial informasi.</li>\r\n	<li>Program edukasi perbankan yang berkelanjutan dengan melalui kerja sama dengan BI dan OJK.</li>\r\n	<li>Program CSR perbankan dengan fokus kepada pendidikan dan pemberdayaan komunitas.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id="sharia-banking-compartment" class="anchor-hww"></div>\r\n<h3>10.   Kompartemen Perbankan Syariah</h3>\r\nGagasan Utama:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Forum Product Manager.</li>\r\n	<li>Shariah Goes To Campus.</li>\r\n	<li>Shariah Award.</li>\r\n	<li>IB Net Perbankan Syariah.</li>\r\n	<li>Sertifikat Bankir Syariah.</li>\r\n	<li>Partisipasi IBEX.</li>\r\n	<li>Kajian Hukum Perbankan Syariah.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Lingkup Kerja', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '906-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-04 11:49:27', '2014-12-04 04:49:27', '', 906, 'http://perbanas.org/id/906-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
