(1816, 8, '2015-01-06 14:07:36', '2015-01-06 07:07:36', 'TEMA:\nPeran Aktif Perbankan dalam Mendorong Perkembangan Industri Subtitusi\nImpor dalam Mewujudkan Ekonomi Berdikari\n\nTempat &amp; Waktu:\nAssembly Hall dan Lower Lobby\nJakarta Convention Center\n28 - 30 Agustus 2014\n\nPerhimpunan Bank - Bank Nasional (PERBANAS)\ndidukung oleh:\n<ul>\n	<li>Bank Indonesia</li>\n	<li>OJK (Otoritas Jasa Keuangan)</li>\n	<li>Himbara (Himpunan Bank Milik Negara)</li>\n	<li>Asbanda (Asosiasi Bank Pembangunan Daerah)</li>\n	<li>Asbisindo (Asosiasi Bank Syariah Indonesia)</li>\n	<li>Perbarindo (Perhimpunan Bank Perkreditan Rakyat Indonesia)</li>\n	<li>Ikatan Bankir Indonesia</li>\n</ul>\nTarget Pasar (Pengunjung dan partisipan) IBEX 2014\n<ul>\n	<li>Kalangan perbankan &amp; finansial beserta penunjang sektor perbankan lainnya seperti IT untuk perbankan, jasa keamanan perbankan, dll.</li>\n	<li>Industri ekonomi kreatif yang akan mampu menciptakan produk substitusi impor untuk menunjang ekonomi berdikari</li>\n	<li>Masyarakat umum termasuk kalangan anak muda dan anak-anak,sebagai sarana edukasi perbankan</li>\n</ul>\n<a href="http://perbanas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Sekilas-IBEX2014.pdf">Sekilas IBEX2014</a>\n<a title="Indonesia Banking Expo" href="http://ibex.or.id" target="_blank">Website Indonesia Banking Expo</a>\n\n<strong>UNDUH MATERI IBEX 2014</strong>', 'Indonesia Banking Expo 2014', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1060-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-06 14:07:36', '2015-01-06 07:07:36', '', 1060, 'http://perbanas.org/1060-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1817, 8, '2015-01-06 14:09:57', '2015-01-06 07:09:57', 'TOPIC:\nThe Important Role of Banking To Encourage the Development of Import Substitution Industry and Creating the Self-Sufficient Economy\n\nDate &amp; Venue:\nAssembly Hall dan Lower Lobby\nJakarta Convention Center\nAugust of 28th-30th, 2014\n\nNational Bank Association – National Bank (PERBANAS)\nsupported by:\n<ul>\n	<li>Bank Indonesia</li>\n	<li>OJK (Otoritas Jasa Keuangan)</li>\n	<li>Himbara (Himpunan Bank Milik Negara)</li>\n	<li>Asbanda (Asosiasi Bank Pembangunan Daerah)</li>\n	<li>Asbisindo (Asosiasi Bank Syariah Indonesia)</li>\n	<li>Perbarindo (Perhimpunan Bank Perkreditan Rakyat Indonesia)</li>\n	<li>Ikatan Bankir Indonesia</li>\n</ul>\nTarget Market (Guests and Participants) IBEX 2014\n<ul>\n	<li>Participants from banking and financial background along with other banking sectors such as IT, Security Service, and so on.</li>\n	<li>Creative economy industry that is capable to create the substitution import products, in order to support the self-sufficient economy.</li>\n	<li>Public spectator, including youths and beginner in banking industry, as the medium for banking education.</li>\n</ul>\nOverview of <a href="http://perbanas.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Sekilas-IBEX2014.pdf">IBEX2014</a>\n<a title="Indonesia Banking Expo" href="http://ibex.or.id" target="_blank">Website Indonesia Banking Expo</a>', 'Indonesia Banking Expo 2014', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-06 14:09:57', '2015-01-06 07:09:57', '', 268, 'http://perbanas.org/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
